<inglise> Article 4 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 4 </eesti>
<inglise> In the case of the derogations provided for in the Annex, the Member States shall be obliged to ensure that employers comply with the following procedures and measures: </inglise>
<eesti> Lisas s&auml;testatud erandite puhul on liikmesriigid kohustatud tagama, et t&ouml;&ouml;andjad j&auml;rgivad j&auml;rgmisi menetlusi ja meetmeid: </eesti>
<inglise> (a) an employer must take adequate precautions to protect the health and safety of the workers concerned; and </inglise>
